, {"text": "(7.0)", "bbox": [814.1, 757.0, 854.0, 777.9]}, {"text": "(7.0)", "bbox": [896.4, 757.0, 936.3, 777.9]}, {"text": "0.0", "bbox": [985.8, 757.2, 1011.9, 778.1]}, {"text": "0.0", "bbox": [1068.1, 757.2, 1094.2, 778.1]}, {"text": "The Company recognizes transfers between input levels as of the actual date of the event. There were no", "bbox": [185.5, 807.2, 1058.6, 828.1]}, {"text": "transfers between input levels during the twelve months ended December 31, 2018.", "bbox": [143.8, 832.2, 840.0, 853.1]}, {"text": "The following methods and assumptions were used to estimate the fair value of each class of financial", "bbox": [185.5, 882.3, 1037.8, 903.1]}, {"text": "instruments reflected in the Consolidated Balance Sheets:", "bbox": [143.8, 907.3, 625.1, 928.1]}, {"text": "Cash Equivalents: Cash equivalents consist of highly liquid short-term investments and term bank deposits,", "bbox": [185.5, 957.1, 1085.5, 978.1]}, {"text": "which mature within three months. The estimated fair value of the Company’s cash equivalents approximates", "bbox": [143.8, 982.3, 1058.1, 1003.1]}, {"text": "their carrying value.", "bbox": [143.8, 1007.3, 312.5, 1028.1]}, {"text": "Short-Term Borrowings: The carrying amounts of the Company’s unsecured lines of credit and commercial", "bbox": [185.5, 1057.1, 1084.4, 1078.2]}, {"text": "paper issuances approximates fair value because of their short maturities and variable interest rates.", "bbox": [143.8, 1082.3, 974.5, 1103.2]}, {"text": "Senior Notes: The Company determines the fair value of its senior notes based on their quoted market value or", "bbox": [185.5, 1132.1, 1087.3, 1153.2]}, {"text": "broker quotes, when possible. In the absence of observable market quotes, the notes are valued using non-binding", "bbox": [143.8, 1157.3, 1070.0, 1178.2]}, {"text": "market consensus prices that the Company seeks to corroborate with observable market data.", "bbox": [143.8, 1182.4, 901.8, 1203.2]}, {"text": "Hedged Fixed Rated Debt: The interest rate swap agreements convert the fixed interest rate to a variable rate", "bbox": [185.5, 1232.2, 1094.1, 1253.2]}, {"text": "based on LIBOR. These agreements are designated as hedges of the changes in fair value of the underlying debt", "bbox": [143.8, 1257.4, 1078.7, 1278.2]}, {"text": "obligation attributable to changes in interest rates and are accounted for as fair value hedges. The fair value of", "bbox": [143.8, 1282.4, 1062.0, 1303.2]}, {"text": "these interest rate swap agreements is reflected in the Consolidated Balance Sheet within Other Current Assets or", "bbox": [143.8, 1307.4, 1090.2, 1328.2]}, {"text": "Accounts Payable and Accrued Expenses, with an offsetting amount recorded in the Current portion of long-term", "bbox": [143.8, 1332.4, 1089.7, 1353.2]}, {"text": "debt to adjust the carrying amount of the hedged debt obligation.", "bbox": [143.8, 1357.4, 684.7, 1378.2]}, {"text": "65", "bbox": [608.6, 1465.8, 629.4, 1486.6]}]}